keyValuePair.Value: Can this team keep it going?
You've put together a decent run of results. How confident are you that this group of players can keep your momentum going?
We'll keep working hard.
We know what we want to achieve and I think this team's good enough to reach our targets. It'll be all about hard work now.
We'll try our hardest, for sure.
We can't tell how the rest of the season will play out, of course. But I know this group of players will give everything to get to where we want to be.
There's a spirit in the squad.
I hope the lads will continue like this
There's a great togetherness in our dressing room. Every player is ready to play his part. That spirit has brought us this far, and it'll carry us through the rest of the campaign, too.

We couldn't have gotten this far without this amazing group of players. They completely understand what is needed and they are willing to fight until the last minute to achieve their goals. I just hope the lads will continue like this.
Can this team make the playoffs now?
Very few people expected to see you in such a strong position. You've got a real chance of playoffs now. Is this team good enough to get you there?
We want to be consistent.
We know where we want to be and, at the moment, we're in the winning habit. I think our players have enough about them to get all the way to the playoffs.
It's a tough league.
This is a very competitive league and it's impossible to tell what's going to happen from one week to the next. But we're going to give it everything to reach the playoffs now.
I think we've got what it takes!
I hope the lads will continue like this
I'm not just going to sit here and tell you what you should already know. These are good players. We're a good team. Anything's possible now.
Can the team do it?
You've got yourselves into a fantastic position, riding high in the table. Can the team sustain its momentum now?
We'll keep playing our football.
We know exactly where we want to be, and I believe this group of players is good enough to get us there. We just need to keep playing our football.
We'll give everything we've got.
There are still so many games to play. It's impossible to tell what the rest of the season will bring. But I promise we'll be giving everything to get over the line.
The lads are united.
I hope the lads will continue like this
The lads have been doing really well and there's a great spirit amongst them. I think that can be key now. Every player's ready to play his part.

We couldn't have gotten this far without this amazing group of players. They completely understand what is needed and they are willing to fight until the last minute to achieve their goals. I just hope the lads will continue like this.
Can your boys compete for the title now?
You've been confounding expectations all season. And now you're in with a title chance. But have your boys got enough to make the most of the opportunity?
We're just taking it game by game.
We haven't got here by making promises. We've just taken one game at a time and it's brought us to the brink of something special. We're positive about things as they stand.
We'll do everything we can.
There are so many things can happen to a team with lots of football still to play. But we're in good shape and we're going to give everything from here on.
It's a special group of players.
I hope the lads will continue like this
It's been our spirit, as much as anything, that's got us in with a title chance. And that's not going to change. Every member of the squad is desperate to give everything he can.

We couldn't have gotten this far without this amazing group of players. They completely understand what is needed and they are willing to fight until the last minute to achieve their goals. I just hope the lads will continue like this.
Can you really go up?
Not many people had you down as promotion challengers. But here you are, in with a real chance. Can your boys keep it going?
We've got a good attitude.
The team's discovered the winning habit and everybody's feeling positive around the club. We've got the mentality to succeed I think.
We want to try to go up.
It's a crazy league and it's impossible to predict what will happen. But I can tell you this group of players is desperate for promotion. They're going to give it everything.
We're desperate to get over the line.
I hope the lads will continue like this
We've been going so well and the boys know the prize is within reach. Every single member of the squad will give his all now to get us over the line.

We couldn't have gotten this far without this amazing group of players. They completely understand what is needed and they are willing to fight until the last minute to achieve their goals. I just hope the lads will continue like this.
Can this team make Europe?
This could be one of the great stories of the season. Against all the odds, your team's in contention for a European place. Can the boys make it now?
We can do it, I believe.
What can I say? We know where we want to be and we're all convinced we've got what it takes to get there. Let's try and keep this great run going now.
All we can do is our best.
There are so many other teams in contention, it's impossible to predict what will happen. But we know European football is a possibility for us and we'll give everything to get there.
We'll need unity now.
I hope the lads will continue like this
This is something we're all fighting for together and every player's going to have to be involved. It's a fantastic group and our spirit can get us over the line.
